    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. Output comparison demonstrates RH index agreement within 20% across all validation operating points. The simplified laminar CFD model is accepted as adequate for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. The exclusion of turbulence modeling is noted in the model form documentation; the laminar assumption is considered conservative for the nominal operating regime. No additional fidelity trade study was deemed necessary by the assessment team.",
